les-section-container flying-files-section-mobile-view " style="--section-height:auto"><div class="flying-files-section-wrapper-mobile no-modal-login-form"><div class="flying-files-content-wrapper"><div class="flying-files-header-text-content mobile-view"><h1 class="flying-files-main-heading"><span>Your data.</span><span class="text-gradient h1-text-gradient"> Your rules.</span></h1><p class="flying-files-sub-heading">Store, access, and manage your files on your own terms, from anywhere.</p></div><div class="flying-files-login-form-and-download-btn-wrapper-mobile"><div class="flying-files-login-form-container-mobile" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(100px)"><div class="flying-files-login-form-wrapper-inner-mobile"><div class="flying-files-signup-form-component-wrapper"><div class="signup-form-slide-container" style="width:100%;opacity:1;transform:none"><div class="signup-form-container login-form-container"><div class="load_wrap loading-signup-form inside-modal"><div class="load_box"></div></div><div class="login-or-signup-form-container"><!--$!--><template data-dgst="BAILOUT_TO_CLIENT_SIDE_RENDERING"></template><!--/$--></div><div class="signup-form-disclaimer">No credit card required</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><section class="section "><div class="align-container  "><div class="image-and-text-section-grid-container image-and-text-section-image-position-left image-and-text-section-mobile-image-position-between has-title has-subtitle has-image  "><div class="image-and-text-section-title " style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)"><h2 class="title align-left align-mobile-center icon-position-left "><span class=""><span>European excellence.</span></span><span class="text-gradient"><span>Swiss privacy.</span></span></h2></div><div class="image-and-text-section-image" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(0.9px)"><img alt="Section image" loading="lazy" width="1084" height="1084" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="img-full-size " style="color:transparent" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, min(100vw, 1180px)" srcSet="//pcdn-www.pcloud.com/ZWdcT/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fanimated-home%2Fswiss-privacy%2Fprivacy%402x.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=90 640w, //pcdn-www.pcloud.com/ZWdcT/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fanimated-home%2Fswiss-privacy%2Fprivacy%402x.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=90 750w, //pcdn-www.pcloud.com/ZWdcT/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fanimated-home%2Fswiss-privacy%2Fprivacy%402x.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=90 828w, //pcdn-www.pcloud.com/ZWdcT/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fanimated-home%2Fswiss-privacy%2Fprivacy%402x.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=90 1080w, //pcdn-www.pcloud.com/ZWdcT/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fanimated-home%2Fswiss-privacy%2Fprivacy%402x.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=90 1200w, //pcdn-www.pcloud.com/ZWdcT/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fanimated-home%2Fswiss-privacy%2Fprivacy%402x.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=90 1920w, //pcdn-www.pcloud.com/ZWdcT/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fanimated-home%2Fswiss-privacy%2Fprivacy%402x.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=90 2048w, //pcdn-www.pcloud.com/ZWdcT/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fanimated-home%2Fswiss-privacy%2Fprivacy%402x.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=90 3840w" src="//pcdn-www.pcloud.com/ZWdcT/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fanimated-home%2Fswiss-privacy%2Fprivacy%402x.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=90"/></div><div class="image-and-text-section-subtitle" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)"><div class="image-and-text-section-text-wrapper subtitle align-left align-mobile-center     "><div><span>We&#x27;re here to provide a reliable, secure cloud storage that puts your privacy first. As a Swiss-based cloud solution, we follow the world’s strictest data privacy standards. And our rock-solid encryption ensures your files are always secure.</span><br/><span> No compromises. No tracking. No third-party access.</span></div><div class="cta-buttons-wrapper" style="align-self:flex-start;--align-self:flex-start;--mobile-align-self:center"><div class="cta-button-wrapper buttons-1 cta-buttons-template-null "><div class="cta-link-wrapper"><a class="link" style="--min-width:max-content;--min-width-mobile:max-content" href="/features/security">Learn more</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class="service-map-section-container " style="--section-background:#FAFAFA"><div class="service-map-container"><div class="service-map-sticky-content"><div class="texts-container"><h2 class="title" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)"><span>Take control.</span><span class="text-gradient">It&#x27;s your data.</span></h2><p class="subtitle" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)"><span>You choose where your files live: </span><span style="font-weight:bold">Europe</span><span> or </span><span style="font-weight:bold">USA</span><span>. Our ultra-secure data centers are certified and built for maximum protection.</span></p><a class="link" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)" href="/data-regions">Learn more</a></div><div class="service-map-map-container" style="opacity:0;filter:blur(10px);transform:scale(0.9)"><div class="service-map-map-wrapper"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 1200 562.3"><g style="filter:drop-shadow(4px 3px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.07))"><path fill="#D5D8DB" d="M1129.4 522a1.9 1.9 0 1 0 0-3.8 1.9 1.9 0 0 0 0 3.8M1129.4 528.9a1.9 1.9 0 1 0 0-3.8 1.9 1.9 0 0 0 0 3.8M1122.5 518.1c-1.1 0-1.9.9-1.9 1.9 0 1.1.9 1.9 1.9 1.9 1.1 0 1.9-.9 1.9-1.9s-.7-1.9-1.9-1.9M1122.5 525c-1.1 0-1.9.9-1.9 1.9s.9 1.9 1.9 1.9c1.1 0 1.9-.9 1.9-1.9s-.7-1.9-1.9-1.9M1122.5 531.8c-1.1 0-1.9.9-1.9 1.9s.9 1.9 1.9 1.9c1.1 0 1.9-.9 1.9-1.9s-.7-1.9-1.9-1.9M1115.7 515.1a1.9 1.9 0 1 0 0-3.8 1.9 1.9 0 1 0 0 3.8M1115.7 522a1.9 1.9 0 1 0 0-3.8 1.9 1.9 0 0 0 0 3.8M1115.7 528.9a1.9 1.9 0 1 0 0-3.8 1.9 1.9 0 0 0 0 3.8M1115.7 542.6a1.9 1.9 0 1 0 0-3.8 1.9 1.9 0 1 0 0 3.8M1108.8 535.7a1.9 1.9 0 1 0 0-3.8 1.9 1.9 0 1 0 0 3.8M1108.8 542.6a1.9 1.9 0 1 0 0-3.8 1.9 1.9 0 1 0 0 3.8M1129.4 453a1.9 1.9 0 1 0 0-3.8 1.9 1.9 0 1 0 0 3.8M1129.4 459.9a1.9 1.9 0 1 0 0-3.8 1.9 1.9 0 